K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:62a-1: pa; bu 'o na khyod ci'i phyir rab tu mi 'byung /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-0: @118a *// sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-1: gang gi tshe 'phags skyes po mi gti mug can gyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-2: ser skya'i gnas na gnas pa'i sh'akya 'khon med pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-4: mi 'khu pa dag bsad pa de'i tshe na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-5: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' po'i sring mo'i bu gnyis shig pha mas bor nas de dang de na 'khyams pa las /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-6: mnyan yod kyi tshong ba dag zong thogs te ser skya'i gnas su dong ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-7: de dag gis de gnyis bzhin gzugs las ngo shes nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-8: khye'u gnyis khyed kyi pha ma gnyis gang na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-10: 'phags skyes po mi gti mug can gyis bsad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-11: mnyan yod na khyed gnyis kyi zhang po btsun pa kun dga' bo zhes bya ba dge slong rab tu grags pa 'dug na ci'i phyir der mi 'dong /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-13: kho bo cag su zhig gis der khrid par 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-15: de dag gis zong bsgyur nas rin blangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-16: khye'u de gnyis khrid nas mnyan yod du song ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-17: de dag gis khye'u de gnyis rgyal byed kyi tshal gyi sgor bor ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-18: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos de gnyis bzhin gzugs las ngo shes nas des smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-19: khye'u gnyis kyi pha ma gnyis gang na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-21: 'phags skyes po mi gti mug can gyis bsad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118a-22: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo nye du la mnyes gshin pa yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-0: des nye du dang bral ba thos nas mchi mas brnangs te 'dug @118b go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-1: dge slong rnams kyis de la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-2: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo khyod kyi khye'u 'di gnyis su dag cig yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-4: khyod ci'i phyir 'di gnyis sdud par mi byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-6: kho bo ni lto 'grangs tsam gyis bsod snyoms blangs nas phyir 'byung na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-7: kho bos 'di gnyis la gang nas sbyin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-9: khye'u 'di gnyis kyis dge slong dag la lo ma dang me tog dang 'bras bu dag 'bul na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-10: dge slong dag kyang 'di gnyis la lhung bzed kyi lhag ma sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-11: des de gnyis bsdus nas dge slong dag la lo ma dang me tog dang 'bras bu dag 'bul du gzhug par brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-12: dge slong dag kyang da gnyis la lhung bzed kyi lhag ma sbyin par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-13: de dag gis de gnyis la zhag nyung shas shig byin nas /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:118b-28: dus las yol bar mi rmad pa /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:119a-2: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:119a-3: dge slong dag ci'i phyir dge slong kun dga' bo skya bo bseng bseng po rid pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:119a-9: bcom ldan 'das tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo'i sring mo'i bu gnyis shig pha mas bor nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo g-yar bltam pa tsam gyi bsod snyoms blangs nas /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:119a-11: phyed ni de gnyis la stsol bas; des na tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo 'di skya bo bseng bseng bo rid pa dang /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:124b-26: 'khor lo bzhin du sbyar ba bklags pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-0: 'phags pa bdag cag gi yang lha dang mi rnams kyi @125a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-4: yi dvags rnams kyi nang du skye bar bgyi'am /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-6: bzhin bzang gnyis 'gro ba lnga po'i 'khor bar ji srid du nyon mongs pa rnams rgyun chad par ma gyur pa de srid du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-7: zo chun rgyud mo'i tshul gyis yongs su 'khor bar bya dgos so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-8: de gnyis yid byung nas tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-9: gang phyir mi gnas lha rnams mi bzang ste //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-10: 'tsho ba thung ba'i mi rnams mi bzang ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-11: gang na zhi med srid pa mi bzang ste //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-12: mya ngan 'das pa mchog ces bde gshegs gsungs //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-13: 'phags pa ci nas kyang bdag 'khor bar 'khor na slan chad nyon mongs pa de lta bu dag kun tu spyod par mi 'gyur ba de ltar bdag cag la chos bstan du gsol /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-14: tshe dang ldan pa mo'u dgal gyi bu chen pos de gnyis kyi bsam pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-17: rang bzhin khong du chud nas gang thos nas de gnyis kyis nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-18: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-19: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa las 'dod chags dang bral ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-20: bong ba dang gser du mnyam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-21: nam mkha' dang lag mthil du mtshungs pa'i sems dang ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-22: tsan dan dang ste'ur mnyam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-23: rig pa'i sgo nga'i sbubs dral bar gyur cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-26: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125a-29: bkur sti la rgyab kyis phyogs pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-0: dbang po dang nye dbang dang bcas pa'i @125b lha rnams kyis mchod par bya ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-2: mngon du smra bar bya bar gyur pa de lta bu'i chos bstan pa byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-3: de gnyis rdzu 'phrul gyis steng gi nam mkha' la me tog dag thu zhing 'dong ba dge slong rnams kyis mthong nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-5: tshe dang ldan pa dag 'di gnyis gang dag yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-6: che ge mo dang che ge mo yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-8: bdag cag lhung bzed nag por zos nas so dag lhung zhing mgo skya bor gyur kyang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-9: bdag cag gis sems rtse gcig pa yang ma thob na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-10: tshe dang ldan pa 'di gnyis dang po lo bdun kho na lon pa de rab tu byung na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-11: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-12: bcom ldan 'das kyis kun dga' bo brtson 'grus kyis byang chub thob bo zhes bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-13: de ni legs par gsungs pa yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-14: dge slong rnams the tshom skyes nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-15: the tshom thams cad gcod pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-16: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-17: btsun pa dge tshul 'di gnyis kyis las ci zhig bgyis na las de'i rnam par smin pas lo bdun kho na lags na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'dul ba la nyan thos rnams kyi bslab pa'i gzhi bca' ba mdzad pa gang lags pa de 'di gnyis kho na la brten nas bag yongs su mdzad cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-20: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:125b-22: dge slong dag 'di gnyis nyid kyis las tshogs rnyed pa rkyen yongs su bsgyur ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-0: 'od pa bzhin du nye bar gnas @126a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-1: pa; gdon mi za bar 'byung bar 'gyur ba dag byas shing bsags pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-2: 'di gnyis nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa dag gzhan su zhig gis myong bar 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-3: dge slong dag las byas shing bsags pa dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-4: phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-7: rlung gi khams la mi 'gyur gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-9: mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa ni zin pa'i phung po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-10: khams dang skye mched dag la rnam par smin par 'gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-11: las rnams bskal pa brgyar yang ni //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-12: chud mi za ba'ang tshogs dang dus //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-13: rnyed na lus can rnams la ni //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-15: dge slong dag sngon byung ba bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid la skye dgu'i tshe lo nyi khri thub pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-16: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-19: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-20: bla na med pa lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-21: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'od srung 'jig rten du byung ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-22: de dge slong gi 'khor nyi khri dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-23: w'a ra n'a si na drang srong smra ba ri dvags kyi nags na nye bar rten cing bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-24: w'a ra n'a si na khyim bdag phan tshun bshes pa gnyis shig gzhon nu'i gnas skabs su rab tu 'byung bar 'dod na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-25: de gnyis kyis nye du dag las rab tu 'byung bar ma thob nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126a-26: gang gi tshe lang tsho yol bar gyur pa de'i tshe na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-0: @126b de gnyis kyis nye du dag la bltas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-1: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gi bstan pa la rab tu byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-3: rtag tu gzhon rims kyis las bya ba yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-4: dge slong rnams kyis rgan zhugs 'di gnyis deng zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-5: rgan zhugs 'di gnyis khyed cig ces bsgo'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-6: de na gcig ni spro ring ba'i rang bzhin can yin cig shos ni spro thung ba'i rang bzhin can yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-7: de khro bar byed pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-9: rgan zhugs gzhon pa'i gnas skabs su rab tu ma byung na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-11: de na 'di gnyis kyis tshe ji srid par tshangs par spyod pa spyad na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-12: yon tan gyi tshogs 'ga' yang ma thob nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-13: de'i 'og tu 'chi ba'i tshe smon lam 'di skad ces bdag cag gis bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yon gnas bla na med pa 'od srung la tshe ji srid par tshangs par spyod pa spyad na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-14: yon tan gyi tshogs 'ga' yang ma thob ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-15: bdag cag gis tshe ji srid par tshangs par spyod pa spyad pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-16: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-17: bram ze'i khye'u bla ma la bram ze'i khye'u khyod ma 'ongs pa'i dus na skye dgu'i tshe lo brgya thub pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-18: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-21: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:126b-22: bla na med pa lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-1: ldan 'das sh'akya thub pa zhes bya bar 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan pa de'i bstan pa la bdag cag le bdun kho na lon nas rab tu byung ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-2: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs pa des 'dul ba la nyan thos rnams kyi bslab pa'i gzhi bca' ba mdzad pa gang yin pa de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-3: bdag cag gnyis kho na la brten nas bag yangs su mdzad cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-4: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du gyur cig ces gdab par brtsams so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-5: dge slong dag de la de'i tshe de'i dus na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-6: khyim bdag gnyis gang dag yin pa de dag ni dge tshul 'di gnyis yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-7: de gnyis kyis der smon lam btab pa gang yin pa des da ltar lo bdun kho na lon nas rab tu byung ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-8: ngas 'dul ba la nyan thos rnams kyi bslab pa'i gzhi bcas pa gang yin pa 'di gnyis kho na la brten nas bag yangs su byas shing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-9: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pa dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-10: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das yul ka shi dag tu ljongs rgyu zhing gshegs pa na phyogs gcig tu byon pa dang 'dzum pa mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-11: chos nyid kyis na gang gi tshe sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams 'dzum pa mdzad pa de'i tshe na; zhal nas 'od zer sngon po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127a-16: shel dang dngul gyi kha dog lta bu dag byung nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-0: kha cig @127b ni steng phyogs su 'dong pas gang dag 'og logs su 'dong ba de dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-1: sems can dmyal ba yang sos dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-14: aud pal ltar gas pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-16: padma ltar gas pa chen por dong ste; sems can dmyal ba tsha ba gang dag yin pa de dag tu bsil bar gyur te 'bab par byed la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-17: sems can dmyal ba grang ba gang yin pa de dag tu dro bar gyur te 'bab par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-18: des sems can dmyal ba de dag gi gnod pa'i bye brag dag rgyun gcod par byed cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-19: de dag 'di snyam du shes ldan dag ci bdag cag 'di nas shi 'phos sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-20: 'on te gzhan du skyes snyam du sems so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-21: de dag dad pa bskyed par bya ba'i phyir /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis sprul pa gtong bar mdzad de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-23: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-24: 'di snyam du shes ldan dag bdag cag 'di nas shi 'phos pa yang ma yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-25: gzhan du skyes pa yang ma yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:127b-26: 'di ltar sems can sngon ma mthong ba 'di'i mthus bdag cag gi gnod pa'i bye brag dag rgyun chad par gyur to snyam du sems so //

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-5: dge slong dag de la de'i tshe de'i dus na dge slong zhal ta byed par gyur pa gang yin pa de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-6: dge slong dge 'dun 'tsho 'di nyid yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-7: de'i lhan cig gnas pa lnga brgya po gang dag yin pa de dag ni drang srong lnga brgya po 'di dag nyid yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-8: ri brags na gnas pa'i skye bo'i tshogs gang dag yin pa de dag ni tshong pa lnga brgya po 'di dag yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-9: 'dis der chos dang ldan pas zhal ta byas pa gang yin pa'i las de'i rnam par smin pas phyug cing nor mang ba longs spyod che ba'i khyim du skyes so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-10: 'chi ba'i dus kyi tshe smon lam btab pa des ni nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-11: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas shing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-12: gdul ba'i don chen po byas par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-13: dge slong dag de ltar na las gcig tu gnag pa rnams kyi rnam par smin pa ni gcig tu gnag pa yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-14: las gcig tu dkar ba rnams kyi rnam par smin pa yang gcig tu dkar ba yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-15: las 'dren ma rnams kyi rnam par smin pa yang 'dren ma yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-16: dge slong dag de lta bas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-17: las gcig tu gnag pa rnams spangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-18: las gcig tu dkar ba rnams la brtsal bar bya ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-19: dge slong dag khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-20: dge slong rnams the tshom skyes nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164a-21: the tshom thams cad gcod pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-0: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la @164b zhus pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-1: btsun pa klu gzhon nu sprul pas dang po gang du dad pa thob par gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-3: dge slong dag bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid la skye dgu'i tshe lo nyi khri thub pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-4: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-7: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-8: bla na med pa lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-9: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'od srung zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-10: de dge slong nyi khri'i 'khor dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-11: w'a ra n'a si na drang srong smra ba ri dvags kyi nags na nye bar brten cing bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-12: de nyan thos rnams la dge slong dag /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-23: bas mtha' gnas mal 'di dag tu bsam gtan gyis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-24: dge slong dag bag yod par bsgrubs la phyis 'gyod par mi 'gyur bar gyis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-25: 'di ni nga'i gdams ngag dang rjes su bstan pa yin no zhes chos ston par mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-26: bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-27: dge slong rnams dgon pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-37: bas mtha'i gnas mal dag tu zhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:164b-38: kha cig ni ri rab kyi bang rim la bsam gtan byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-0: @165a *// kha cig ni gser gyi ri bdun po dag na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-1: kha cig ni mtsho chen po ma dros pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-2: kha cig ni rdzing bu dal gyis 'bab pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-3: kha cig ni rnal 'byor pa'i skye bo dang rjes su mthun pa'i grong dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-6: rgyal po'i pho brang gi phyogs de dang de dag na bsam gtan byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-7: ji tsam na klu gzhon nu skyes nas ring po ma lon pa zhig 'dab chags kyi rgyal po 'dab bzang gis ri rab kyi bang rim gyi steng du drangs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-8: ji tsam na des dge slong spyod lam zhi bas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-11: rnal 'byor la rjes su brtson pa dag mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-12: mthong nas kyang de'i sems mngon par dad par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-13: de sems dad pa skyes nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-14: 'phags pa bdag nyid chen po 'di dag ni sdug bsngal gyi bye brag 'di lta bu las grol ba yin no snyam du sems bskyed par byed cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-15: de de dag la sems mngon par dad par byas nas dus la bab pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-16: las drug la brtson pa'i bram ze'i khyim zhig tu skyes nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-17: ji tsam na bsrings shing bskyed de chen por gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-19: bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gi gsung rab la rab tu byung nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-22: brtsal bas nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-23: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-24: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa las 'dod chags dang bral ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165a-25: bong ba dang gser du mnyam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-0: nam mkha' dang lag mthil du mtshungs pa'i sems @165b dang ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-1: tsan dan dang ste'ur mnyam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-2: rig pas sgo nga'i sbubs dral bar gyur cing rig pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-4: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-7: bkur sti la rgyab kyis phyogs pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-8: dbang po dang nye dbang dang bcas pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod par bya ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-10: mngon du smra bar byas par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-14: las gang gis byas snyam na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-15: des dud 'gro nas shi 'phos shing mi rnams kyi nang du skyes pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-16: nyan thos chen po rnams la sems mngon par dad par byas pas skyes par mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-17: des pha ma la bsams te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-18: bdag gi pha ma ga la 'dug snyam na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-19: klu'i gnas na 'dug par mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-20: ci byed snyam na klu'i skye gnas na ngu zhing 'dug par mthong nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-21: des rdzu 'phrul gyis der song ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-23: yab yum ci'i slad du bshums /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-25: 'phags pa bdag cag gi klu gzhon nu skyes nas ring po ma lags pa zhig 'dab chags kyi rgyal po 'dab bzang gis phrogs na de gar mchis ma 'tshal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-27: yab yum de ni bdag nyid lags te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-28: shi zhing dus la bab nas las drug la brtson pa'i bram ze'i khyim du skyes te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-29: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gi bstan pa la rab tu byung nas nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du bgyis so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-30: 'phags pa de 'dra bar skyon chags par gyur pa de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:165b-31: bdag cag gis bde 'gror mchi bar yang ma bsams na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-0: @166a *// dgra bcom pa lta ci smos te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-1: de ni ngo mtshar dang rmad du byung ba lags na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-2: khyod kyis yon tan gyi tshogs de lta bu brnyes sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-4: 'phags pa khyod ni bsod snyoms bzhed pa lags la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-5: bdag cag ni bsod nams 'tshal ba lags kyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-6: khyod 'di nyid du gdugs re re zhing gshegs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-7: zhal zas kyi bya ba mdzod la bzhud cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-8: de dang du blangs nas des rtag par klu'i gnas su bdud rtsi zos shing ldog par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-9: de lhan cig gnas pa'i dge tshul de la dge slong rnams kyis smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-10: dge tshul khyod kyi mkhan po 'di gang du zos shing 'ong /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-14: klu'i gnas su lha'i bdud rtsi zos shing zos shing 'ong na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-17: de ni rdzu 'phrul che ba mthu che ba lags pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-21: gang gi tshe 'di rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro ba de'i tshe na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-22: khyod kyis 'di'i chos gos kyi grva nas zung zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-25: bzhin bzang gal te de'i chos gos kyi grva la ri'i rgyal po ri rab btags na de yang mi ltung na khyod lta ci smos /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-26: de dag gis de spro bar byas nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-27: gnas gang du de rdzu 'phrul gyis mi snang bar byed pa der song ste bsdad pa dang de yang mi snang bar byed nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-28: des kyang chos gos kyi grva nas bzung ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166a-29: de gnyis steng gi nam mkha' la dong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-0: ji tsam na klu rnams kyis mthong nas de gnyis kyi phyir stan gnyis bshams shing dkyil 'khor yang @166b gnyis byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-2: ci'i phyir stan bshams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-4: des rgyab tu blta bar brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-5: ji tsam na dge tshul de mthong nas des smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-12: lha'i bdud rtsi zhu bar nus na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-13: 'phags pa 'dis ni zhu bar mi nus kyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-14: 'di la kha zas tha mal pa sbyin par bya'o snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-15: de rnams kyis gcig la ni lha'i bdud rtsi byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-16: dge tshul la ni kha zas tha mal pa byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-17: dge tshul de de'i lhung bzed thogs pa yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-18: des mkhan po la lhung bzed blang ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-19: de 'bras chan gyi gzegs ma gcig chags nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-20: dge tshul des de khar bcug ste myangs na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-23: klu rnams ni ser sna can yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-24: lhan cig tu 'khod pa gnyis la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-25: gcig la ni lha'i bdud rtsi byin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-26: gcig la ni kha zas tha mal pa byin no snyam mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-27: de nas de mi bzod pa skyes bas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-28: bdag gis bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yon gnas bla na med pa 'od srung gi spyan sngar tshangs par spyod pa spyad pa gang yin pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag klu 'di gnas 'di nas nyams par byas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-29: 'di nyid du skye bar gyur cig ces smon lam log pa btab bo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:166b-30: las shin tu chen po yongs su rdzogs pa dag ni lus rje ba la mi ltos pas tshe 'di nyid la de'i lag pa gnyis nas chu 'dzag par gyur cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-1: de yang klad pa'i nad kyis btab par gyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-3: 'phags pa dge tshul 'dis sems mi bzang ba bskyed kyis 'di zlog cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-4: des dge tshul de la 'di skad ces smras so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-5: bu 'di dag la sems mi bzang ba bskyed pa zlog cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-6: des tshigs su bcad pa smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-7: sems 'di thag ring gyur pa ste //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-9: bdag gi lag na chu 'dzags pas //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-10: bzlog par bgyi ba mi nus so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-11: des klu de gnas de nas nyams par byas nas de nyid du skyes te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-12: dge slong dag klu gzhon nu sprul pas dang po der dad pa thob par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-13: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-14: rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-15: ji tsam na mu stegs can zhig rgyal byed kyi tshal du phyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-16: des de na stan bzang po bshams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-17: bza' ba dang btung ba bsod pa'i spyi bungs bshams pa mthong nas des bsams pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-18: zang zing gi longs spyod ni sh'akya'i bu'i dge sbyong 'di dag gi bzang la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-19: chos kyi longs spyod ni bdag cag gi bzang bas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-20: de'i phyir 'di dag gi nang du rab tu byung la zang zing gi longs spyod ni 'dir bya zhing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-21: chos kyi longs spyod ni der bya'o snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-22: de dge slong gi gan du song ste smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-23: 'phags pa bdag rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-24: des de rab tu phyung zhing bsnyen par rdzogs par byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-25: mu stegs can rnams kyi gso sbyong ni bcu bzhi ba yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167a-26: dge slong rnams kyi gso sbyong ni bco lnga pa yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-0: de @167b tshes bcu bzhi la ni mu stegs can rnams kyi gso sbyong nyams su myong bar byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-1: tshes bco lnga la ni dge slong rnams kyi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-2: ji tsam na dus gzhan zhig na zhag bri bar gyur na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-3: dge slong rnams kyi gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa la bab pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-4: de la the tshom skyes te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-6: 'on te 'di nyid du gso sbyong nyams su myong bar bya snyam pa las /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-7: de la blo skyes pa sh'akya'i bu'i dge sbyong 'di dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-8: des pa 'grogs na bde ba yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-9: bdag gi tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa rnams ni ngang tshul ngan pa yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-10: gal te ma song na bdag gi tshul shing yang phyung bar 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-11: spang la khri'u yang bsgyur bar 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-12: slong phor yang khas phub par 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-14: tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa rnams kyi nang nas kyang phyung bar 'gyur ro snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-15: de mu stegs can rnams kyi nang du song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-16: ji tsam na dge skos rgan pa'i mtha' logs su 'greng ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-17: dge slong rnams la bsngos pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-18: de mi snang nas des dri bar brtsams pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-19: tshe dang ldan pa dag dge slong ming 'di zhes bya ba zhig 'dir 'ongs sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-21: de dag gis smras pa ma 'ongs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis phyogs bzhir bltas nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-23: gso sbyong bya'o zhes bka' stsal pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-24: dge slong de dag gis phyogs bzhir bltas te gso sbyong byas so; ;de'i 'og tu phyi de nyin par dge slong de 'ongs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-25: dge slong rnams kyis smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-26: tshe dang ldan pa khyed gang nas 'ongs /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:167b-28: tshangs pa mtshungs pa dag gi gan nas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-1: mtshungs par spyod pa dag su yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-2: mu stegs can dag yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-3: kho bo zang zing gi longs spyod ni khyod cag gi gan du byed la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-4: chos kyi longs spyod ni de dag gi gan du byed do zhes zer ba'i skabs de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-5: bcom ldan 'das la dge slong rnams kyis gsol ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-6: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-7: dge slong dag gang zag 'di ni mu stegs can zhugs pa yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-8: dge slong dag gang zag mu stegs can zhugs pa ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-9: chos 'dul ba 'di la mi skye ba'i chos can yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-10: dge slong dag khyod kyis gang zag mu stegs can zhugs pa chos 'dul ba 'di la bsnyil bar bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-11: 'ga' zhig gi gan du rab tu 'byung bar 'dod pa 'ongs na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-12: des de la mu stegs can zhugs pa ma yin nam zhes dri bar bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-13: ma dris par rab tu 'byin par byed na 'gal tshabs can du 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-14: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la tshe dang ldan pa nye bar 'khor gyis zhus pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-15: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das kyis gang zag mu stegs can zhugs pa chos 'dul ba 'di las bsnyil bar bya'o zhes bka' stsal nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-16: btsun pa ji tsam gyis na gang zag mu stegs can zhugs pa bsnyil bar bgyi ba lags /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-17: nye 'khor gang tshun chad nas rgyal mtshan 'di 'chang zhing lta ba de la dga' bas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-18: der skya rengs 'char bar byed na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-19: de tsam gyis na gang zag mu stegs can zhugs pa bsnyil bar bya ba yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168a-20: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-0: rgyal byed kyi @168b tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-1: mnyan yod na khyim bdag gcig 'dug pa des /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-2: rigs mnyam pa las chung ma blangs nas de dang de lhan cig rtse bar byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-7: dga' mgur spyod par byed pa de'i bu byung nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-8: des chung ma la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-9: bzang mo'u bu cag gi bu lon 'khor bar byed pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-11: kho bo zong thogs te yul gzhan du 'gro bar bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-13: rje'i sras de bzhin mdzod cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-14: de zong thogs te yul gzhan du song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-15: de nyid du tshul ma yin pas sdug bsngal bar gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-16: des kyang bu de nye du'i stobs dang lag mthus bsnyod cing gsos te bskyed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-18: ne'u ldangs dang lhan cig khyim zhig gi drung du song ba na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-19: khyim de'i steng na bu mo zhig 'dug pa des /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-20: steng du me tog gi chun po 'phangs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-21: des bu mo de mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-23: grogs po khyod kyis khyim der brda ma byas sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-28: grogs po khyim 'di ni yang ba yin gyis ma 'jug cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-29: tshul ma yin pas sdug bsngal bar gyur ta re zhes des nyin thog thag tu 'phyan du bcug ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-30: ma'i gan du khrid nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-31: ma khyod kyi bu 'dis che ge mo zhig tu brda byas pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-32: kho bos nyin thog thag tu bsrungs kyis mtshan mo srungs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-33: khyim de ni yang ba yin gyis 'jug tu ma gzhug cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:168b-34: tshul ma yin pas sdug bsngal bar gyur ta re /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-1: kyis kho mo la bsnyad pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-2: khyod kyis legs pa byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-3: des khye'u de khyim gyi nang du mal bcas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-5: chu dang sa dag bzhag nas khyim der bcug ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-6: bdag nyid sgor khri bcas pas nyal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-7: des smras pa ma sgo phye shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-11: bu 'di nyid du kho mos gyo mo gzhag gis der gcis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-12: des yud tsam zhig bsdad de smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-17: bu 'di nyid du kho mos gyo mo dang chu dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-18: sa gzhag gis 'di nyid du bshang ba byos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-19: des yang yud tsam zhig bsdad de smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-22: bu khyod gang du 'gro 'dod pa kho mos mi shes sam ci /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-23: kho mos sgo dbye bar mi nus so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-24: ma kho bos khyod gsad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-26: bu kho mo shi ba ni bla'i /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-27: kho mo bu shi ba la lta ni mi phod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-28: 'dod pa bsten pas ni sdig pa'i las mi bya ba ci yang med pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-29: snying rje med pa'i sems dang ldan pa 'jig rten pha rol btang ba des /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-30: ral gri shugs nas phyung ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-31: de'i mgo drung nas bcad de sa la bsgyel to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-32: des ma bsad nas song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-33: sems can sdig pa'i las byas pa 'dar bas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-34: bu mo des de la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-35: rje'i sras 'di na su yang ma mchis te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-36: bdag bu mo dang gnyis su bas kyi ma bsnyengs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-38: de 'di la smras na dga' bar 'gyur ro snyam nas des smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169a-39: bzang mo kho bos khyod kyi phyir ma bsad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-4: 'di yon tan dag mngon par mi shes te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-6: gang gi tshe bdag la khro ba skyed na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-7: bdag la gnas skabs ci zhig 'byung bar 'gyur snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-9: rje'i sras bdag steng gi khang thog tu 'dzegs nas slar mchis pa'i bar du re zhig yud tsam zhig gzhes shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-12: de nas steng gi khang thog tu 'dzegs nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-13: chom rkun pa chom rkun pa zhes sgra phyung ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-14: de 'jigs shing skrag nas bros te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-15: rang gi khyim du song nas sgo drung du ral gri bzhag ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-16: chom rkun pa de ni 'di yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-17: kho bo'i ma bsad nas bros so zhes sgra phyung nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-18: des de'i ma'i ro de bkur sti byas te song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-19: sems can sdig pa'i las byas pas ni brtan pa mi rnyed pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-20: de mu stegs can gyi gnas dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-21: dka' thub kyi gnas de dang de dag tu song ste dris pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-22: shes ldan dag las ci zhig byas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-24: de na kha cig na re /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-25: mer zhugs shig ces zer ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-26: kha cig na re dug zo zhig ces zer ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-27: kha cig na re g-yang sar mchongs shig ces zer ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-28: kha cig na re thag pas 'gags te shi zhig ces zer te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-29: thams cad kyang shi ba'i thabs ston par byed kyi nges par 'byung ba'i thabs ston pa ni 'ga' yang med do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-31: rgyal byed kyi tshal du song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-32: des de na dge slong zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-33: gang gis sdig pa'i las byas pa //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-34: dge ba yis ni 'gog byed de //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:169b-35: nyi zla sprin nas byung ba ltar //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-2: zhes kha ton zer ba thos nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-4: sdig pa'i las kyang dgag par nus kyi 'di dag gi gan du rab tu 'byung ngo snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-5: de dge slong gi gan du song ste smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-6: 'phags pa bdag rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-7: des de rab tu phyung zhing bsnyen par rdzogs par byas nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-8: de shin tu brtson 'grus brtsams te bklags par brtsams so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-9: des klog cing kha ton byed pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-10: sde snod gsum bklags shing sde snod gsum dang ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-11: rig pa dang grol ba'i spobs pa can du gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-12: de la dge slong dag gis smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-13: tshe dang ldan pa khyod brtson 'grus 'dis ci zhig don du gnyer /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-15: sdig pa'i las zad par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-16: khyod kyis sdig pa'i las ci byas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-21: skyed ma mo yin no zhes zer ba'i skabs de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-22: bcom ldan 'das la dge slong rnams kyis gsol pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-23: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-24: dge slong dag 'di ni gang zag ma bzad pa bsnyil bar 'os pa yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-25: dge slong dag gang zag ma bsad pa ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-26: chos 'dul ba 'di la mi skye ba'i chos can yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-28: gang zag ma bsad pa chos 'dul ba 'di las bsnyil bar bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-29: 'ga' zhig gi gan du rab tu 'byung bar 'dod pa 'ongs na des de la ma bsad pa ma yin nam zhes dri bar bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170a-30: ma dris par rab tu 'byin par byed na 'gal tshabs can du 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-2: mtha' 'khob tu 'gro bar bya snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-4: khyim bdag gcig rjes su 'jug par byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-6: de'i phyir gtsug lag khang brtsig tu bcug ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-7: de phyogs dang yul tha dad pa na 'khod pa'i dge slong dag gnas shing de'i gdams ngag gis mang po dag gis dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-8: de dus gzhan zhig na na bar gyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-13: 'bras bu'i sman dag gis rim gror byas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-14: nyams dmas pa nyid du gyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-15: des lhan cig gnas pa rnams la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-16: tshe dang ldan pa dag kho bo'i phyir dge 'dun la bsro khang gyis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-17: de rnams kyi de'i phyir bsro khang byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-18: bsags pa kun gyi mtha' zad cing //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-19: mthon po rnams kyi mtha' ltung 'gyur //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-20: phrad pa'i mtha' ni bral pa ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-21: gson pa'i mtha' ni 'chi pa yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-23: de shi zhing dus la bab nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-24: sems can dmyal pa chen po mnar med par skyes so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-25: de'i lhan cig gnas pa dgra bcom pa zhig gis bdag gi mkhan po gang du skyes zhes sems par zhugs nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-26: des lha rnams kyi nang du rnam par blta par brtsams nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-30: yi dvags rnams kyi nang du rnam par bltas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-32: sems can dmyal pa'i nang du rnam par blta par brtsams na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:170b-33: sems can dmyal pa chen po mnar med par skyes par mthong nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-1: mkhan po ni tshul khrims dang ldan pa mang du thos pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-2: chos kyi 'khor sdud sdud pa yin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-3: des las ci zhig byas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-4: des sems can dmyal ba chen po mnar med par skyes snyam nas bsams na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-5: ma bsad pa yin par mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-6: de mnar med pa'i 'od zer dag gis phog pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-8: kye ma bsro khang 'di me re tsha zhes smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-9: sems can dmyal ba'i srung mas tho ba blangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-11: skal chad khyod kyi bsro khang ga la yod /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-12: 'di ltar 'di ni sems can dmyal ba chen po mnar med pa yin no zhes smras so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-13: de dge ba'i sems kyis dus la bab nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-14: rgyal chen bzhi'i ris kyi lha rnams kyi nang du skyes so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-15: lha'i bu'am lha'i bu mo'i chos nyid ni skyes nas ring po ma lon pa la sems gsum skye ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-19: des sems can dmyal ba rnams kyi nang nas shi 'phos ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-20: rgyal chen bzhi'i ris kyi lha rnams kyi nang du skyes pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-21: dge 'dun la bsro khang gi khrus byas pas skyes pa mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-22: de nas sngon sems can dmyal ba lha'i bu de 'di snyam du sems te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-23: gang gi phyir bdag zhag lon par gnas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-24: bcom ldan 'das la blta ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-25: bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir nye bar 'gro ba ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-26: bdag gi tshul dang mthun pa ma yin gyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-27: bdag zhag lon par ma gnas pa kho nar bcom ldan 'das la blta ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171a-28: bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir nye bar 'gro'o snyam mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-0: de nas sngon sems can dmyal ba lha'i bu @171b rna cha gdub bgor [?] g-yo zhing dri ma med par thogs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-1: do shal dang se mo dos brgyan pa'i lus kyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-5: padma dkar po dag gis thu ba bkang ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-6: kha dog shin tu 'das pas mtshan mo la bab pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-7: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-8: bcom ldan 'das la me tog dag gis mngon par gtor ta [*te?]/
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-9: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs gnyis la mgo ngos phyag 'tshal nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-11: 'di ltar sngon sems can dmyal ba lha'i bu'i kha dog gi mthus /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-12: rgyal byed kyi tshal thams cad snang ba rgya chen pos khyab par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-13: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sngon sems can dmyal ba lha'i bu'i bsam pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-15: khams dang rang bzhin thugs su chud nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-16: gang thos nas sems can dmyal ba lha'i bus stan de nyid la 'dug bzhin du 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo nyi shu mtho ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-17: ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-18: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu mngon sum du byas pa de lta bur 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi yang dag par so sor rtog par byad pa'i chos bstan par mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-20: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag la gang mdzad pa 'di lta bu ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-21: bdag la las kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-24: lha rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-25: sngon gyi pha mes dag gis kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:171b-26: dge sbyong dang bram ze dag gis kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-2: rtsa lag gi tshogs kyis kyang ma bgyis te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-3: khrag dang mchi ma'i rgya mtsho ni bskams /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-4: rus pa'i ri dag las ni bsgral /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-5: ngan song gi sgo dag ni bkum /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-6: mtho ris dang thar pa'i sgo dag ni phye /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-9: yi dvags dag nas ni rkang pa phyung /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-10: lha dang mi rnams kyi nang du bzhag go zhes lan gsum ched du brjod pa ched du brjod do; ;yang smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-11: khyod mthus rab drag nyes pa mang ldan pa'i //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-12: ngan song shul bkag bsod nams rab ldan pa'i //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-13: mtho ris 'gro ba phye zhing bdag gis ni //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-14: mya ngan 'das pa'i shul ni thob par gyur //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-15: shin tu rnam dag khyod brten bdag gis ni //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-16: de ring skyon bral dag pa'i mig thob cing //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:172a-17: go 'phang zhi ba 'phags pa dgyes thob ste //

K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-0: @372a *// bslab pa'i gzhi rnams mnos so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-1: gang gi tshe yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gis sangs rgyas kyi mdzad ba mtha' dag mdzad nas phung po lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-2: rgyal po kri kris de'i mchod rten rin po che sna bzhi las khor khor yug tu dpag tshad gang tsam la 'phang du dpag tshad phyed pa zhig byed du bcug nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-3: de zhig cing gogs pa dag slar bcos pa'i phyir grong khyer gyi shar phyogs kyi sgo nas dpya 'du ba gang yin pa de dag des mchod rten de la phul lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-4: gang gi tshe rgyal po kri kri shi nas de'i bu legs skyes zhes bya ba de rgyal srid la bzhag pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-5: de'i blon po dag gis dpya nyung shas shig phul lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-6: des blon po rnams la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-7: ci'i phyir khyod kyis nga la dpya nyung du zhig phul /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-8: nga'i yul nas dpya mi 'du'am zhes smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-10: lha dpya de las 'du ba ga la mchis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-11: lha grong khyer gyi shar phyogs kyi sgo nas dpya 'du ba gang lags pa de dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-12: rgyal po yab kyis mchod rten zhig cing gogs pa slar bcos pa'i rgyur bzhag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-14: dpya de bdag cag gis dgum mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-16: shes ldan nga'i yab kyis gang mdzad pa de ni tshangs pas byas pa'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372a-17: de ni brgya byin gyis byas pa'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-0: gal te lhas mi gnang na bdag cag gis ci nas dpya de dag rang 'du bar @372b mi 'gyur ba de ltar bya'o snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-1: de dag gi sgo bcad de bzhag pas phyin chad dpya 'du ba chad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-2: mchod rten de yang zhig cing gogs par gyur pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-3: khyo shug de gnyis rgas pa gyur pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-4: mchod rten de nyid la byi bdar byed cing 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-5: byang phyogs nas ded dpon zhig zong thogs nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-6: w'a ra n'a si'i grong du phyin pa dang des mchod rten zhig cing gogs par gyur pa de mthong ngo; ;de mthong nas yab yum mchod rten 'di su'i lags zhes dris so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-8: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gi yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-11: rgyal po kri kri des mchod rten zhig pa dang gogs pa slar bcos pa'i phyir phul ba cung zad med dam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-14: grong khyer gyi shar phyogs kyi sgo nas dpya 'du ba gang dag mchod rten de zhig pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-15: gogs pa bcos pa'i phyir phul ba las rgyal po kri kri nongs nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-16: de'i sras legs skyes zhes bya ba de rgyal srid la bzhag nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-17: des dpya 'du ba de bcad pas mchod rten de zhig cing gogs par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-18: des rin po ches spras pa'i rna cha rna ba las phral nas des de gnyis la byin te smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-19: yab yum rin po che'i rna cha 'dis mchod rten 'di zhig cing gogs pa rnams chos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-20: bdag nam zong rnams 'gyur te 'ongs nas phyis kyang sbyin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:372b-21: de gnyis kyis de btsongs nas des mchod rten de zhig pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-2: de nas dus phyis shig na ded dpon gyis zong bsgyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-4: des mchod rten de blta bas mi ngoms pa zhig tu mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-5: mthong nas kyang de'i phyir zhing rab tu dga' ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-6: dang ba skyes te dris pa yab yum khyed kyi skyin po cung zad ma byas sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-8: bu bdag cag gis skyin pa cung zad kyang ma byas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-9: 'on kyang lhag pa yang yod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-10: de rab tu dang ba skyes nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-11: de la ci lhag pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-18: longs spyod che ba'i rigs su skye ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-20: ston pa 'di lta bu kho na mnyes par byed kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-21: mi mnyes par mi byed par gyur cig ces smon lam btab bo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-22: dge slong dag 'di ji snyam du sems /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-23: ded dpon gang yin pa de ni gro bzhin skyes rna ba byi ba ri 'di nyid yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-24: 'dis gang yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gi mchod rten la bya ba byas te; smon lam btab pa'i las de'i rnam par smin pas phyug pa dang nor mang ba dang longs spyod che ba'i rigs dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-25: rin po ches spras pa'i rna cha rna ba la thogs bzhin du btsas shing nga'i bstan pa la rab tu byung nas nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-26: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373a-27: 'dis yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-0: stobs mnyam @373b pa; brtson pa mnyam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-1: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa brnyes pa'i ston pa nga mnyes par byas kyis ma mnyes par ni ma yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-2: dge slong dag de lta bas na las gcig tu gnag pa rnams kyi rnam par smin pa ni gcig tu gnag pa yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-3: gcig tu dkar ba rnams ni dkar ba yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-4: 'dren ma rnams ni 'dren ma yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-5: dge slong dag de lta bas na las gcig tu gnag pa rnams dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-7: las gcig tu dkar ba kho na la brtsal bar bya ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-8: dge slong dag khyed kyis de lta bu la bslab par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-9: btsun pa tshe dang ldan pa gro bzhin skyes rna ba bye ba ris las ci zhig bgyis na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-10: las de'i rnam par smin pas mthong bas chos 'di nyid la ngan song dag mthong ba lags /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-12: 'dis ma la ngag gi las rtsubs po smras pa de'i las de'i rnam par smin pas mthong ba'i chos nyid la ngan song dag mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-13: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rgyal po rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-14: tshe dang ldan pa nye dga' dge 'dun gyi gsar bu yin pas de gral rims kyi khri ldeg pa zhig thob pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-15: de zhig gis dogs pas bla 'og ma bsgyur bas nyal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-17: bdag nye dga' yin na khri la yang chags sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-19: khri ma rjes na nye dga' zhes bya ba'i ming yang mi 'dogs so snyam nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:373b-20: de nang par sngar langs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-0: @374a *// yul ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyi drung du song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-2: btsun pa nye dga' byon pa legs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-4: ji ga btsun pa nye dga' bde bar gzims sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-6: gsus po che khyod ji snyam du sems /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-7: ji ltar bdag mal stan rim pa brgyad la nyal ba bzhin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-8: nye dga' yang de bzhin snyam mam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-9: kho bo dge 'dun gyi gsar bu yin pas kho bo gral rims kyis khri ldeg pa zhig thob ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-10: de zhig gis dogs nas kho bos bla 'og kyang mi bsgyur bar nyal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-11: btsun pa nye dga' mal stan rim pa brgyad po 'di 'dra ba brtags lags sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-16: gal te brtags ba lags na dbul gyis snoms la bzhud cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-18: gsus po che ko sa la'i yul rnams kho bo dbang ngam ci /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-19: gtsug lag khang du skyol la byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-20: des de la mi brgyad byin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-21: de la bzhis ni mal stan rnams khyer /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-22: bzhis ni khri khyer nas de dag srang gi dbus nas dong ba bram ze dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-23: khyim bdag de dag gis mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-25: shes ldan dag deng lha'i gzims mal gang du byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374a-29: nye dgas smras pa 'di dag ni bdag gis thob bo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-0: @374b shes ldan dag dge sbyong nye dga' ni 'dod pa'i yon tan gyis dbyen spyo'am ci /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-1: zhes de dag smod par byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-4: de gtsug lag khang du song nas gtsug lag khang du chag chag btab /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-6: ba'i lci ba sar pa'i byug pas byugs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-7: gnas mal bshams nas nyal bar bsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang phyogs der byon to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-9: de dga' ba skyes nas bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-10: btsun pa bdag gis gnas mal ci 'dra bar mchis gzigs su gsol /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-11: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-12: dge slong dag thog ma nyid du rul ba sbed pa ni skyes bu gti mug nye dga' yin par rig par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-14: nyes dmigs gang ci byung ba de ni dge slong dag khri stan mthon po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-15: khri stan chen po la nyal ba yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-16: de lta bas na dge slong gis khri stan mthon po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-17: khri stan chen po la 'dug par mi bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong gis khri stan mthon po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-20: khri stan chen po la 'dug par mi bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-22: khyim bdag gzhan zhig gis sangs rgyas la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun khyim du spyan drangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:374b-23: de khri stan mthon po dag bshams par brtsams so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-1: dang ldan pa kun dga' bo sngon rol nyid du son pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-2: des stan mthon po dag shom pa de mthong nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-4: khyim bdag stan 'di dag ni dge slong dang 'tsham pa ma yin gyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-6: des de dag bsdu bar brtsams pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyang der gshegs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-8: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni mkhyen bzhin du rmed pa yin pas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la rmas pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-9: kun dga' bo 'di ci zhig byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-11: khyim bdag 'dis chen po la 'os pa'i gdan dag shom nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-12: bdag gis khyim bdag stan 'di dag ni dge slong dang 'tsham pa ma yin gyis 'di dag sdus shig ces bsgo ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-13: de de dag sdud pa lags so;/
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-14: kun dga' bo thams cad la 'byor pa yod pa ma yin gyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-15: kun dga' bo khyim bdag stan shom pa la ma zlog cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-16: de lta bas na rjes su gnang ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-17: khyim du khri stan mthon po la 'dug par bya'i /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-18: der nyal bar ni mi bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-19: gtsug lag khang du ni 'dug par mi bya nyal bar mi bya ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-20: 'dug gam nyal na 'gal tshabs can du 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-21: lho phyogs nas dge slong chos gos gsum pa gzhan zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-22: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal du mnyan yod du 'ongs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375a-23: de'i bags pa'i gding ba bzang po da nye dgas mthong nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-0: @375b des de la smras pa bsod snyoms pa pags pa kho bo la byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-1: kho bo bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal du 'gro'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-3: btsun pa nye dga' 'gro yang rung mi 'gro yang rung /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-4: bdag bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal du 'dir 'ongs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-5: bsod snyoms pa khyod ji snyam du sems /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-6: nye dgas 'o ni 'dra ba'i pags pa rnyed par mi nus snyam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-7: nga'i rnyed pa la ltos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-9: btsun pa nye dga' khyod kyis gang gi phyir nus pa de'i phyir kho bo mi 'bul lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-10: yul ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyi ba lang gi spyan byed pa chen po zhes bya ba dang tshe dang ldan pa nye dga' bshes pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-11: de de'i gan du song ba na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-12: ji tsam na sos ka'i dus su be'u bkra zhing bkra ba dag byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-13: des be'u gcig gis rgyab tu byugs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-15: btsun pa nye dga' khyod be'u 'di'i ma'i 'o ma gsol bar bzhed dam ci /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-17: de yang 'dod mod kyi 'di 'dra ba'i pags pa dge slong gang la yod pa ni sems las chung ngus bde bar dge ba'i phyogs la rab tu brtson par 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-19: btsun pa nye dga' bka' stsal pas 'dzal gyis bzhud cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-20: de song ba dang chen pos phyugs rdzi la bsgo ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-21: be'u 'di sod la khyod kyis pags pa khyer te btsun pa nye dga' la phul cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:375b-22: des be'u de bsad nas pags pa khyer te song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-1: la dungs pas skad 'byin cing rjes bzhin du song ba las /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-2: de rgyal byed kyi tshal du zhugs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-3: ba de rgyal byed kyi tshal gyi sgo na skad 'byin cing 'dug go ;sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni mkhyen bzhin du rmed pa yin pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-4: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-6: rgyal byed tshal gyi sgo na ba 'di ci'i phyir skad 'byin cing 'dug /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-7: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos gsol pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-8: bcom ldan 'das btsun pa nye dgas be'u de'i pags pa 'tshal ba'i slad du 'gum stsal bas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-9: des na ba de rgyal byed kyi tshal gyi sgo na skad 'byin lags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-11: nyes dmigs gang ci byung ba de ni dge slong dag ko lpags 'chang ba yin gyis de lta bas na dge slong gis ko lpags bcang bar mi bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-12: bcangs na 'gal tshabs can du 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong gis ko lpags bcang bar mi bya'o zhes gsungs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-14: khyim bdag gzhan zhig gis sangs rgyas la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun khyim du gdugs tshod la spyan drangs na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-15: khyim bdag des gdan gzhan bsham du med nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-16: des ko lpags kyi gdan dag bsham par brtsams so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376a-17: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo nang par sngar langs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376b-0: khyim bdag de'i khyim du song ba @376b dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376b-1: des khyim bdag de ko lpags kyi gdan dag shom pa mthong nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-001-001:376b-2: khyim bdag stan 'di dag ni dge slong dang 'tsham pa ma yin gyis 'di dag sdus shig /
